SurPro,SURS2M2030,,"SurPro 20-30"" Magnesium Double Sided Stilt",simple,"<h2>Elevate Your Workflow with SurPro S2 Precision Stilts</h2> <p>Experience the pinnacle of professional-grade stability with the SurPro S2 Magnesium Double-Sided Stilts. Engineered for the demanding drywall contractor, these stilts redefine job-site efficiency by minimizing fatigue and maximizing balance. By utilizing a sophisticated double-sided pole architecture, the S2 series provides a rock-solid foundation that allows you to maneuver with confidence, whether you are hanging board, taping, or finishing ceilings.</p> <h2>Unmatched Comfort and Structural Integrity</h2> <p>Designed to withstand the rigors of daily heavy-duty use, the S2 features a lightweight yet incredibly durable magnesium-alloy frame. The innovative 360-degree wraparound leg bands move in harmony with your natural gait, eliminating the pressure points common in traditional single-pole designs. With a fully customizable fit—including adjustable calf height, footbed length, and lean tension—these stilts adapt to your specific biomechanics, ensuring you remain productive from the first hour to the last.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Interlock Safety System:</strong> Patented redundancy technology provides peace of mind by securing all critical stress points during operation.</li> <li><strong>Hex-Extruded Frame:</strong> The unique hexagonal geometry offers superior structural rigidity while maintaining a lightweight profile for all-day wear.</li> <li><strong>Double-Clamshell Design:</strong> Enhances lateral stability and prevents the twisting motion often found in standard stilts, ensuring a consistent, balanced stance.</li> <li><strong>Precision Adjustability:</strong> Features comprehensive customization for leg band positioning, footplate length, and forward/backward lean tension.</li> <li><strong>High-Traction Soles:</strong> Industrial-grade, non-marking rubber soles deliver exceptional grip on both residential and commercial flooring surfaces.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | Model | S2 Magnesium Double Sided |<br /> | SKU | SURS2M2030 |<br /> | Height Range | 20"" - 30"" |<br /> | Max Load Capacity | 225 lbs (per pair) |<br /> | Frame Material | Magnesium Alloy |<br /> | Safety System | Interlock Enhanced Safety System |<br /> | Sole Type | Non-marking, High-Grip Rubber |</p>",SurPro set the bar and then broke it with the invention of double-sided drywall stilts. The newly updated SurPro S2 maximizes everyday performance by further elevating your comfort and stability.,,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surs2m2030.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilts,"30"", drywall stilts, magnesium, SurPro",1439,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS1010R,,SurPro Double Sided Right Leg Band Kit,simple,"<h2>Restore Your Stability and Performance</h2> <p>Maintain the professional-grade reliability of your equipment with the SurPro S2 Right Leg Band Kit. Engineered specifically for seamless integration with standard SurPro Double-Sided Stilts, this replacement component ensures your gear remains secure, comfortable, and fully operational during demanding work shifts. Whether you are performing routine maintenance or replacing a worn-out part, this genuine SurPro component provides the exact fit and structural integrity required for safe operation at height.</p> <h2>Precision Engineering for SurPro Stilts</h2> <p>Designed to meet the rigorous demands of drywall professionals and contractors, this leg band kit is crafted to provide consistent support and ergonomic alignment. By utilizing authentic replacement parts, you preserve the balance and safety standards inherent in your SurPro stilts. Please note that this specific kit is tailored for the standard S2 series and is not compatible with the S2X model, which utilizes the specialized Rocker Leg Band system.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Genuine Compatibility:</strong> Specifically engineered for all generations of SurPro Double-Sided Stilts (excluding S2X models).</li> <li><strong>Right-Side Configuration:</strong> Precision-molded to fit the right leg assembly for optimal comfort and secure attachment.</li> <li><strong>Durable Construction:</strong> Built to withstand the high-impact, heavy-duty environment of professional job sites.</li> <li><strong>Easy Installation:</strong> Designed for straightforward replacement, minimizing downtime so you can return to the task at hand quickly.</li> <li><strong>Safety-Focused Design:</strong> Ensures the structural integrity of your stilt setup, maintaining the manufacturer's intended performance standards.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | Product Name | Double Sided Right Leg Band Kit |<br /> | SKU | SURSS1010R |<br /> | Compatibility | All SurPro Double-Sided Stilts (Excluding S2X) |<br /> | Side | Right |<br /> | Part Type | Replacement Leg Band Kit |</p>","This S2 Leg Band Kit (Right) works with all generations of SurPro Double-Sided Stilts, except the S2X, which features our Rocker Leg Bands. This part is the Right Leg Band only.",,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss1010r.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,SurPro,1440,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS1010L,,SurPro Double Sided Stilts Leg Band Kit,simple,"<h2>Restore Your Stability and Performance</h2> <p>Ensure your SurPro Double-Sided Stilts remain in peak operating condition with this genuine replacement Left Leg Band. Engineered for durability and a secure fit, this component is essential for maintaining the balance and safety required for professional-grade drywall and ceiling work. By replacing worn or damaged leg bands, you restore the structural integrity of your equipment, allowing you to work with confidence and precision.</p> <h2>Seamless Compatibility</h2> <p>Designed specifically for the SurPro S2 series, this replacement part integrates perfectly with your existing setup. Whether you are performing routine maintenance or repairing a damaged unit, this OEM-quality component ensures your stilts continue to provide the reliable support you expect on the job site. Please note that this specific kit is designed for the left leg and is compatible with all standard SurPro Double-Sided Stilts, excluding the S2X model which utilizes the specialized Rocker Leg Band system.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Genuine OEM Replacement:</strong> Manufactured to exact factory standards to ensure a perfect fit and reliable performance.</li> <li><strong>Optimized for S2 Series:</strong> Specifically engineered for compatibility with all generations of SurPro Double-Sided Stilts.</li> <li><strong>Enhanced Safety:</strong> Replacing worn bands prevents slippage and instability, keeping you secure while working at height.</li> <li><strong>Easy Installation:</strong> Designed for straightforward replacement, minimizing downtime so you can get back to your project quickly.</li> <li><strong>Durable Construction:</strong> Built to withstand the rigors of daily professional use in demanding construction environments.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | Product Name | Double Sided Stilts Leg Band Kit (Left) |<br /> | SKU | SURSS1010L |<br /> | Compatibility | All SurPro Double-Sided Stilts (Excludes S2X) |<br /> | Position | Left Leg |<br /> | Part Type | Replacement Leg Band |</p>","This S2 Leg Band Kit (Left) works with all generations of SurPro Double-Sided Stilts, except the S2X, which features our Rocker Leg Bands. This part is the Left Leg Band only.",,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss1010l.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,"drywall stilts, SurPro",1441,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS2007,,SurPro Floor Plate w/ Super Grip Soles Kit,simple,"<h2>Elevate Your Stability and Performance</h2> <p>Experience unparalleled control and confidence while working at height with the SurPro Flexion Floor Plate and Super Grip Sole Kit. Engineered for professionals who demand reliability, this comprehensive set provides the essential components to maintain your equipment's traction and structural integrity. Whether you are performing routine maintenance or tackling demanding job site tasks, these components ensure your stilts remain responsive and secure underfoot.</p> <h2>Precision Engineering for Demanding Environments</h2> <p>This kit is designed to restore the fluid movement and firm footing required for precision work. By replacing worn components with these high-quality SurPro parts, you minimize slippage and maximize the natural flexion of your movement. The included Super Grip Soles are crafted to provide superior surface contact, effectively reducing the risk of accidental slips on various flooring types, while the robust hardware ensures a secure, long-lasting fit.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Enhanced Traction:</strong> The Super Grip Soles are engineered to provide maximum surface adhesion, ensuring stability across diverse work environments.</li> <li><strong>Complete Restoration Kit:</strong> Includes all necessary hardware, such as bolts, washers, springs, and bushings, for a comprehensive maintenance solution.</li> <li><strong>Optimized Flexion:</strong> Designed to maintain the natural, ergonomic movement of your stilts, reducing fatigue during extended use.</li> <li><strong>Durable Construction:</strong> Built with high-grade materials to withstand the rigors of daily professional use.</li> <li><strong>Easy Installation:</strong> All components are precision-machined for a seamless fit, allowing for quick and efficient equipment servicing.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | Product Name | Flexion Floor Plate w/ Super Grip Soles Kit |<br /> | SKU | SURSS2007 |<br /> | Kit Contents | 2x Flexion Floor Plates, 4x Super Grip Soles, Mounting Hardware (Bolts, Washers, Springs, Bushings) |<br /> | Compatibility | Standard SurPro Flexion Stilts |</p>","Flexion Floor Plate w/ Super Grip Soles, Pair. Includes two (2) Flexion Floor Plates, bolts and washers, springs and bushing, (4) Super Grip Soles w/ mounting screws.",,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss2007.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,SurPro,1442,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS1012,,SurPro Foot Plate Kit,simple,"<h2>Elevate Your Stability and Control</h2> <p>Experience superior balance and confidence while working at height with the SurPro Foot Plate Kit. Engineered for professionals who demand reliability, these oversized foot plates provide an expansive, stable platform that accommodates any boot size. By increasing the surface area, SurPro ensures a more secure stance, reducing fatigue and enhancing your overall control during extended periods of use.</p> <h2>Versatile Mounting for Custom Security</h2> <p>What sets the SurPro system apart is its innovative, dual-position arch strap configuration. Beyond the standard top-mounted setup, these plates feature a secondary mounting point located behind the heel. This unique design locks your foot into place, preventing slippage and providing a locked-in feel that traditional plates simply cannot match. Built with high-strength, reinforced geometry, these plates are designed to withstand the rigors of daily job site abuse while maintaining structural integrity.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Oversized Foot Bed:</strong> A wider surface area improves weight distribution and provides a more stable foundation for users of all sizes.</li> <li><strong>Dual-Position Arch Straps:</strong> Choose between traditional top-mounting or the secure heel-locking position for enhanced stability.</li> <li><strong>Professional-Grade Durability:</strong> Crafted with advanced, high-impact geometry to ensure long-term performance in demanding environments.</li> <li><strong>SurPro Exclusive:</strong> Proprietary design elements engineered specifically to outperform standard industry alternatives.</li> <li><strong>Universal Compatibility:</strong> Designed to integrate seamlessly with your existing stilts for an immediate upgrade in safety and comfort.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | Product Name | SurPro Foot Plate Kit |<br /> | SKU | SURSS1012 |<br /> | Quantity | Pair (2 Plates) |<br /> | Mounting Options | Dual-position arch strap capability |<br /> | Construction | High-impact reinforced geometry |</p>",Foot Plate Kit (Pair). Customers love that our foot plates are wider than the other guys. Our larger foot bed is more stable and helps with balance no matter how big or small the user's feet are.,,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss1012.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,SurPro,1443,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS1009,,SurPro Heel Bracket Kit,simple,"<h2>Restore Your Stability and Performance</h2> <p>Ensure your professional-grade stilts remain in peak operating condition with the SurPro Heel Bracket Kit. Designed for precision and durability, this replacement set provides the essential support required for safe, balanced movement while working at height. Whether you are performing routine maintenance or replacing worn components, these genuine SurPro parts guarantee a seamless fit and reliable performance on the job site.</p> <h2>Engineered for Reliability</h2> <p>Crafted to meet the rigorous demands of drywall professionals and contractors, these heel brackets offer the structural integrity needed for long-term use. The adjustable design allows for a customized fit, ensuring your stilts provide optimal comfort and control throughout your workday. By choosing authentic SurPro replacement parts, you maintain the safety standards and mechanical precision your equipment was built to deliver.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Genuine OEM Quality:</strong> Manufactured specifically for SurPro stilts to ensure perfect compatibility and factory-standard performance.</li> <li><strong>Complete Maintenance Set:</strong> Includes two adjustable heel brackets and four mounting screws (HS110W) for a comprehensive, ready-to-install solution.</li> <li><strong>Enhanced Stability:</strong> Provides critical heel support, reducing fatigue and improving balance during extended periods of use.</li> <li><strong>Adjustable Design:</strong> Engineered to accommodate various user preferences, allowing for precise calibration of your stilt setup.</li> <li><strong>Durable Construction:</strong> Built to withstand the high-impact, heavy-duty environment of professional construction and renovation projects.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | Product Name | Heel Bracket Kit |<br /> | SKU | SURSS1009 |<br /> | Included Components | 2 x Heel Brackets, 4 x Screws (HS110W) |<br /> | Compatibility | Genuine SurPro Stilts |</p>",Adjustable Heel Bracket Kit w/ Screws (Pair). Includes (2) Heel Brackets w/ (4) Screws (HS110W). Genuine SurPro Stilts Part.,,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss1009.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,SurPro,1444,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS1006,,SurPro Key & Lock Side Pole Clamp & Bracket Kit,simple,"<h2>Restore Your Stability and Performance</h2> <p>Ensure your drywall stilts remain in peak operational condition with the SurPro Key &amp; Lock Side Pole Clamp and Bracket Kit. Designed specifically for professionals who demand reliability on the job site, this comprehensive hardware set provides the essential components needed to secure your side poles, maintaining the structural integrity and balance required for safe, high-altitude work.</p> <h2>Precision Engineering for S1 and S1X Models</h2> <p>This kit is engineered to meet the exact specifications of SurPro S1 and S1X stilts, ensuring a seamless fit and hassle-free installation. By replacing worn or damaged clamping components, you eliminate unwanted movement and instability, allowing you to focus on your craft with complete confidence. Each component is built to withstand the rigors of daily construction environments, providing a long-lasting solution for your equipment maintenance needs.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Complete Hardware Solution:</strong> Includes a full set of two side pole clamps, two outer metal clamp brackets, and two side pole bolt assemblies for a total system refresh.</li> <li><strong>Optimized Compatibility:</strong> Specifically manufactured for perfect integration with SurPro S1 and S1X stilt models.</li> <li><strong>Enhanced Structural Security:</strong> Effectively locks side poles into place to prevent slippage and maintain consistent height adjustments.</li> <li><strong>Professional-Grade Durability:</strong> Constructed from high-quality materials designed to endure the heavy-duty demands of professional drywall and painting applications.</li> <li><strong>Simplified Maintenance:</strong> Streamlines the repair process, allowing for quick field adjustments and reduced downtime.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | SKU | SURSS1006 |<br /> | Compatibility | S1 &amp; S1X Stilts |<br /> | Included Components | 2x Side Pole Clamps (HP129W), 2x Outer Metal Clamp Brackets, 2x Side Pole Bolt Assemblies (HS124W) |<br /> | Kit Quantity | Pair |</p>","Key & Lock Side Pole Clamp and Bracket Kit w/ Hardware (Pair) - (2) Side Pole Clamps (HP129W), (2) Outer Metal Clamp Brackets, (2) Side Pole Bolt Assemblies (HS124W). Fits: S1 & S1X Stilts",,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss1006.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,SurPro,1445,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS1004O,,SurPro Main Body Spring Kit,simple,"<h2>Restore Your Stilt Performance</h2> <p>Ensure your equipment remains in peak operating condition with the SurPro Main Body Spring Assembly Kit. Designed specifically for professionals who rely on consistent, responsive performance, this kit provides the essential components needed to maintain the tension and stability of your stilts. By replacing worn or fatigued springs, you restore the natural bounce and structural integrity required for safe, efficient movement on the job site.</p> <h2>Precision Engineering for Reliability</h2> <p>This comprehensive set includes everything necessary to service one full pair of stilts. Each component is manufactured to meet rigorous standards, ensuring a seamless fit and reliable operation under demanding conditions. Whether you are performing routine maintenance or addressing a loss of tension, this kit offers a straightforward, high-quality solution to keep your gear performing like new.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Complete Maintenance Solution:</strong> Includes two high-tension springs and all necessary mounting hardware to service a full pair of stilts.</li> <li><strong>Optimized Performance:</strong> Restores the original spring-back action, reducing fatigue and improving balance during extended use.</li> <li><strong>Professional Grade:</strong> Engineered for durability and consistent tension, meeting the high standards expected by drywall and construction professionals.</li> <li><strong>Easy Installation:</strong> Designed for a precise fit, allowing for quick replacement so you can minimize downtime.</li> <li><strong>Genuine Compatibility:</strong> Specifically configured for seamless integration with SurPro stilt systems using the HS145W-O hardware specification.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | Product Name | Main Body Spring Kit |<br /> | SKU | SURSS1004O |<br /> | Hardware Included | HS145W-O |<br /> | Kit Contents | 2 Springs with Hardware |<br /> | Application | One pair of stilts |</p>",Main Body Spring Assembly Kit. (2) Springs w/ Hardware (HS145W-O). Complete set for one pair of stilts.,,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss1004o.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,SurPro,1446,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS1007,,SurPro Nylon Sleeve Kit,simple,"<h2>Elevate Your Stilt Performance</h2> <p>Ensure your SurPro stilts remain in peak operating condition with this comprehensive Nylon Sleeve Kit. Designed for durability and smooth articulation, these replacement components are essential for maintaining the stability and fluid movement required for professional drywall, painting, and ceiling installation work. By replacing worn sleeves, you restore the precision and reliability of your equipment, allowing you to work with confidence and efficiency on every job site.</p> <h2>Precision Engineering for Professional Results</h2> <p>This kit is engineered to meet the exact tolerances of SurPro equipment, ensuring a seamless fit and hassle-free installation. Constructed from high-grade, wear-resistant nylon, these sleeves provide the necessary friction reduction for consistent stilt performance. Whether you are performing routine maintenance or refurbishing a well-used pair of stilts, this kit provides the high-quality components needed to extend the lifespan of your gear.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Complete Maintenance Solution:</strong> Includes a full set of four top and four bottom sleeves to service a pair of stilts entirely.</li> <li><strong>Durable Construction:</strong> Manufactured from industrial-grade nylon designed to withstand the rigors of daily professional use.</li> <li><strong>Optimized Performance:</strong> Restores smooth, quiet operation to your stilt joints, minimizing drag and improving balance.</li> <li><strong>Perfect Compatibility:</strong> Specifically engineered for SurPro stilt systems, ensuring an exact fit without the need for modifications.</li> <li><strong>Essential Replacement:</strong> Ideal for contractors looking to maintain safety standards and equipment longevity.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | Product Name | Nylon Sleeve Kit |<br /> | SKU | SURSS1007 |<br /> | Kit Contents | 4x Top Sleeve (HS148M), 4x Bottom Sleeve (HS149M) |<br /> | Material | Industrial Nylon |<br /> | Compatibility | SurPro Stilts |</p>",Nylon Sleeve Kit (Pair). Includes: (4) Nylon Sleeve Top (HS148M) and (4) Nylon Sleeve Bottom (HS149M).,,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss1007.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,SurPro,1447,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS1005P,,SurPro Plastic Leg Band Kit for Single Sided Stilts,simple,"<h2>Upgrade Your Comfort and Mobility</h2> <p>Experience a new standard of stability and ease while working at heights with the SurPro Flex Leg Band Kit. Designed to replace rigid, traditional aluminum components, these flexible nylon bands provide a forgiving fit that moves with your body, significantly reducing fatigue during long shifts on the job site. Whether you are a professional drywaller, painter, or contractor, this kit ensures your stilts feel like a natural extension of your legs.</p> <h2>Engineered for Performance</h2> <p>The secret to the superior comfort of this kit lies in its high-durability nylon construction. Unlike standard metal bands that can dig into the skin, the Flex Leg Bands offer a contoured, flexible interface that maintains structural integrity while providing a more ergonomic experience. The included wider straps are specifically engineered to distribute pressure more evenly across the inner leg, preventing chafing and discomfort throughout the workday.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Flexible Nylon Construction:</strong> Durable, lightweight material that offers a more forgiving fit than traditional aluminum alternatives.</li> <li><strong>Enhanced Ergonomics:</strong> Wider leg straps minimize pressure points and improve overall comfort during extended use.</li> <li><strong>Comprehensive Kit:</strong> Includes everything needed for a complete upgrade, including two flex bands, two straps, and a full hardware set.</li> <li><strong>Broad Compatibility:</strong> Designed to integrate seamlessly with Sur-Stilts and Sur-Mag models.</li> <li><strong>Versatile Application:</strong> Compatible with newer generation S1 and S1X models as a comfortable, non-OEM alternative to standard wraparound bands.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | SKU | SURSS1005P |<br /> | Included Components | 2x Flex Leg Bands (HS101W-F), 2x Leg Band Straps (HS104S-B), 1x Bolt Kit (SS134) |<br /> | Material | High-Durability Nylon |<br /> | Compatibility | Sur-Stilts, Sur-Mag, S1, S1X |<br /> | Product Type | Stilt Accessory Kit |</p>","Flex Leg Band Kit (Pair). Includes: (2) Flex Leg Bands (HS101W-F), (2) Leg Band Straps (HS104S-B), Leg Band Bolt Kit w/ Washers and Nuts (SS134).",,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss1005p.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,"drywall stilts, SurPro",1448,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS1002B,,SurPro Single Sided Stilts Strap Kit,simple,"<h2>Restore Your Stability and Performance</h2> <p>Ensure your equipment remains in peak condition with the SurPro Single Sided Stilts Strap Kit. Designed to provide a secure, reliable fit, this comprehensive replacement set restores the integrity of your stilts, allowing you to work with confidence and precision. Whether you are performing routine maintenance or replacing worn-out components, this kit delivers the professional-grade durability required for demanding job sites.</p> <h2>Engineered for Reliability</h2> <p>Each component in this kit is crafted to meet the rigorous standards of trade professionals. By replacing frayed or damaged straps, you eliminate unnecessary movement and instability, promoting better balance and safety during extended use. The included hardware ensures a seamless installation process, getting you back to work with minimal downtime.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Comprehensive Replacement:</strong> Includes a full set of leg, arch, and toe straps to completely refresh your single-sided stilt system.</li> <li><strong>Secure Fastening:</strong> Each strap features high-quality buckles designed to maintain tension and prevent slippage throughout the workday.</li> <li><strong>Durable Construction:</strong> Built to withstand the wear and tear of daily construction and drywall environments.</li> <li><strong>Complete Hardware Included:</strong> Comes with all necessary screws and washers, ensuring a quick and secure attachment to your existing equipment.</li> <li><strong>Universal Compatibility:</strong> Specifically engineered to fit all standard SurPro single-sided stilt models.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | SKU | SURSS1002B |<br /> | Compatibility | All Single Sided Stilts |<br /> | Color | Black |<br /> | Included Components | 2 Leg Band Straps (HS104S-B), 2 Arch Straps (HS107S), 2 Toe Straps (HS108W), Mounting Hardware |</p>","Complete Strap Kit for all Single Sided Stilts, Black.",,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss1002b.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,"drywall stilts, SurPro",1449,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS1001,,SurPro Stilt Hardware Kit,simple,"<h2>Restore Your Mobility and Stability</h2> <p>Ensure your professional-grade stilts remain in peak operating condition with the SurPro Stilt Hardware Kit. Designed specifically for maintenance and repair, this comprehensive set provides the essential components required to keep your equipment functioning smoothly on the job site. By replacing worn-out fasteners and bearings, you can maintain the precision balance and safety standards necessary for high-altitude tasks.</p> <h2>Precision Engineering for Reliable Performance</h2> <p>Don't let loose hardware compromise your safety or efficiency. This kit is engineered to meet the rigorous demands of daily construction and drywall work, offering a seamless fit for your existing SurPro equipment. Each component is manufactured to withstand the mechanical stress of constant movement, ensuring your stilts provide consistent support throughout your shift.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Comprehensive Maintenance:</strong> Includes a complete set of 8 high-strength nuts and bolts to secure critical connection points.</li> <li><strong>Smooth Operation:</strong> Comes with 16 premium leg bearings to restore fluid motion and reduce friction during use.</li> <li><strong>Direct Compatibility:</strong> Specifically curated for SurPro stilt systems to ensure a perfect, hassle-free installation.</li> <li><strong>Safety First:</strong> Facilitates the regular maintenance required to prevent equipment failure and maintain structural integrity.</li> <li><strong>Professional Grade:</strong> Built to endure the heavy-duty environment of professional contracting and renovation projects.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | Product Name | Stilt Hardware Kit |<br /> | SKU | SURSS1001 |<br /> | Included Fasteners | 8 sets of nuts &amp; bolts |<br /> | Included Bearings | 16 leg bearings |</p>","SurPro Stilt Hardware Kit includes: 8 sets of nuts & bolts, 16 leg bearings.",,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss1001.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,"drywall stilts, SurPro",1450,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS2004,,SurPro Stilt Socks w/ All Models-Large,simple,"<h2>Elevate Your Comfort on the Job</h2> <p>Experience unparalleled support during long hours on your stilts with SurPro Stilt Socks. Engineered specifically for professionals who demand stability and relief, these socks are designed to mitigate the friction and pressure associated with extended stilt use. By providing a cushioned barrier between your feet and your equipment, they ensure you can maintain focus on your craft without the distraction of discomfort.</p> <h2>Engineered for the Professional Tradesperson</h2> <p>Whether you are performing drywall installation, painting, or ceiling work, your footwear is the foundation of your productivity. These socks feature a specialized construction that conforms to the foot, preventing bunching and slippage inside your stilt straps. The durable fabric blend is optimized for breathability and moisture management, keeping your feet cool and dry throughout the most demanding shifts.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Ergonomic Design:</strong> Tailored specifically for the unique fit requirements of stilt users to minimize pressure points.</li> <li><strong>Enhanced Cushioning:</strong> Provides targeted padding to absorb impact and reduce fatigue during prolonged standing.</li> <li><strong>Moisture-Wicking Fabric:</strong> Advanced materials pull sweat away from the skin, promoting a dry and hygienic environment.</li> <li><strong>Secure Fit:</strong> Engineered to stay in place, preventing the irritation caused by shifting fabric inside your gear.</li> <li><strong>Universal Compatibility:</strong> Designed to integrate seamlessly with all SurPro stilt models and most standard professional stilts.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | Product Name | SurPro Stilt Socks |<br /> | SKU | SURSS2004 |<br /> | Size | Large |<br /> | Compatibility | All SurPro Stilt Models |</p>",Sur-Pro Stilt Socks,,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss2004.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,"drywall stilts, SurPro",1451,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS2005,,SurPro Stilt Socks w/ All Models-XL,simple,"<h2>Elevate Your Comfort and Performance</h2> <p>Experience unparalleled support during long hours on the job site with SurPro Stilt Socks. Engineered specifically for professionals who rely on stilts for drywall, painting, or ceiling installation, these socks provide the essential cushioning and moisture management required to maintain peak productivity while minimizing foot fatigue.</p> <h2>Designed for the Demanding Professional</h2> <p>These socks are crafted to integrate seamlessly with all SurPro stilt models, ensuring a secure fit that prevents bunching or slippage inside the foot plate. By providing an extra layer of protection against the pressure points common with extended stilt use, they allow you to focus entirely on your craftsmanship rather than discomfort.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Stilt-Optimized Fit:</strong> Specifically engineered to accommodate the unique requirements of professional stilts, ensuring stability and comfort.</li> <li><strong>Enhanced Cushioning:</strong> Targeted padding reduces impact and pressure, protecting your feet during high-intensity work shifts.</li> <li><strong>Moisture-Wicking Fabric:</strong> Advanced textile construction draws perspiration away from the skin, keeping your feet dry and comfortable throughout the day.</li> <li><strong>Universal Compatibility:</strong> Designed to perform flawlessly with all SurPro stilt models, making them an essential addition to your gear.</li> <li><strong>Durable Construction:</strong> Built to withstand the rigors of daily construction environments while maintaining their shape and support.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | Product Name | SurPro Stilt Socks |<br /> | SKU | SURSS2005 |<br /> | Size | XL |<br /> | Compatibility | All SurPro Stilt Models |</p>",Sur-Pro Stilt Socks,,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/w