SurPro,SURSS134,,SurPro Stilts Leg Band Bolt Kit,simple,"<h2>Secure Your Stability on the Job</h2> <p>Maintain the structural integrity of your SurPro single-sided stilts with this essential hardware replacement kit. Engineered for durability and a precise fit, this bolt kit ensures your leg bands remain securely fastened, providing the confidence and stability required for professional drywall, painting, and ceiling work.</p> <h2>Reliable Hardware for Demanding Environments</h2> <p>Don't let worn or missing hardware compromise your safety or productivity. This comprehensive kit provides all the necessary components to restore your equipment to factory-standard performance. Each piece is selected for its resistance to the rigors of daily construction use, ensuring a tight, vibration-resistant connection that keeps you moving safely throughout your shift.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Complete Hardware Set:</strong> Includes everything needed for a full leg band replacement, featuring four cap screws, four locknuts, and eight washers.</li> <li><strong>Precision Engineering:</strong> Designed specifically for SurPro single-sided stilts to ensure perfect thread compatibility and fitment.</li> <li><strong>Enhanced Security:</strong> The included locknuts provide superior resistance against loosening, even during repetitive motion and heavy-duty use.</li> <li><strong>Durable Construction:</strong> High-quality materials designed to withstand the high-stress environment of professional job sites.</li> <li><strong>Easy Installation:</strong> Streamlined components allow for quick maintenance, minimizing downtime so you can get back to work faster.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | SKU | SURSS134 |<br /> | Compatibility | Single-Sided Stilts |<br /> | Bolt Type | 1/4""-20 x 2"" Cap Screws |<br /> | Kit Contents | 4 Cap Screws, 4 Locknuts, 8 Washers |</p>","Leg Band Bolt Kit for Single-Sided Stilts. Includes: (4) 1/4""-20 x 2"" Cap Screws, (4) Locknuts and (8) Washers.",,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss134.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,"drywall stilts, SurPro",1453,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS124,,SurPro Stilts Lower Side Pole Bolt Kit,simple,"<h2>Maintain Your Stability and Safety</h2> <p>Ensure your SurPro stilts remain in peak operating condition with this essential hardware replacement kit. Designed specifically for the lower side pole assembly, these components provide the structural integrity required for professional-grade performance. Whether you are performing routine maintenance or replacing worn hardware, this kit ensures your side poles are securely fastened to the main body bracket for reliable, wobble-free operation.</p> <h2>Precision Engineering for Professional Use</h2> <p>Don't compromise on the safety of your equipment. This kit includes high-strength fasteners engineered to withstand the rigors of daily job site use. By utilizing the correct hardware, you prevent unnecessary play in the stilt assembly, allowing for consistent balance and confidence while working at height. Each component is selected to match the exact specifications of your SurPro equipment, ensuring a seamless fit and straightforward installation.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Complete Hardware Set:</strong> Includes everything needed to secure both lower side poles, featuring two cap screws, two locknuts, and four washers.</li> <li><strong>Secure Fastening:</strong> High-quality locknuts ensure that vibrations from movement do not loosen the connection over time.</li> <li><strong>Exact Compatibility:</strong> Specifically manufactured for SurPro stilts to ensure proper alignment with the lower side pole bracket.</li> <li><strong>Durable Construction:</strong> Built to withstand the mechanical stress and environmental demands of professional drywall and construction environments.</li> <li><strong>Easy Maintenance:</strong> Simplifies the repair process, allowing you to get back to work quickly with minimal downtime.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | SKU | SURSS124 |<br /> | Component Type | Lower Side Pole Bolt Kit |<br /> | Fastener Size | 1/4""-20 x 1-1/2"" |<br /> | Included Hardware | (2) Cap Screws, (2) Locknuts, (4) Washers |</p>","These Lower Side Pole Bolts secure your side poles to the Lower Side Pole Bracket on the Main Body of your sets. (2) 1/4""-20 x 1-1/2"" Cap Screws w/ (2) Locknuts and (4) Washers.",,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss124.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,"drywall stilts, SurPro",1454,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS132,,SurPro Stilts Side Pole Clam Bolt Kit,simple,"<h2>Restore Your Stability and Performance</h2> <p>Ensure your SurPro stilts remain in peak operating condition with this essential Side Pole Clamp Bolt Kit. Designed specifically for the rigorous demands of professional drywall and painting work, this hardware kit provides the necessary components to maintain a secure, wobble-free connection between your side poles and the stilt frame. Don't let loose or worn-out hardware compromise your safety or efficiency on the job site; this direct-fit replacement kit restores the structural integrity of your equipment, allowing you to work with confidence and precision.</p> <h2>Precision Engineering for Professional Reliability</h2> <p>Crafted to meet the exact manufacturing standards of SurPro equipment, these bolts are built to withstand the high-torque environments of daily construction use. By replacing worn or stripped fasteners, you eliminate unwanted play in the leg assembly, ensuring consistent balance and support throughout your shift. This kit is a must-have for any professional contractor looking to extend the service life of their stilts and maintain optimal performance standards.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Direct OEM Compatibility:</strong> Engineered specifically for SurPro stilts to ensure a perfect fit and seamless installation.</li> <li><strong>Enhanced Structural Security:</strong> Replaces worn hardware to eliminate side-pole movement and maintain rigid stability.</li> <li><strong>Professional-Grade Durability:</strong> Constructed from high-strength materials designed to resist the wear and tear of demanding work environments.</li> <li><strong>Easy Maintenance:</strong> Allows for quick, on-site repairs, minimizing downtime and keeping you productive.</li> <li><strong>Essential Safety Component:</strong> Helps prevent equipment failure by ensuring all critical connection points are properly tightened and secure.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | Product Name | Stilts Side Pole Clam Bolt Kit |<br /> | SKU | SURSS132 |<br /> | Compatibility | SurPro Stilts Series |</p>",SurPro Stilts Side Pole Clam Bolt Kit,,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss132.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,"drywall stilts, SurPro",1455,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS1011B,,SurPro Stilts Strap Kit w/ Black Laces,simple,"<h2>Restore Your Stability and Performance</h2> <p>Ensure your SurPro stilts remain in peak operating condition with this comprehensive replacement strap kit. Designed specifically for S2 and S2X models, this set provides a complete refresh of your critical connection points, allowing you to maintain the secure, locked-in feel necessary for professional-grade work. Whether you are replacing worn-out components or performing routine maintenance, these high-quality black straps deliver the durability and reliability required for demanding job sites.</p> <h2>Engineered for Durability</h2> <p>Each component in this kit is built to withstand the rigors of daily use, featuring robust buckles and high-tensile materials that keep your equipment firmly attached. By replacing frayed or damaged straps, you eliminate unnecessary movement and enhance your balance, significantly improving safety and comfort during extended periods of use. This kit includes all necessary hardware, ensuring a straightforward installation process so you can get back to work with confidence.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Complete Refresh:</strong> Includes a full set of leg, arch, and toe straps to restore your stilts to factory-standard security.</li> <li><strong>Precision Fit:</strong> Engineered specifically for seamless compatibility with SurPro S2 and S2X stilt models.</li> <li><strong>Durable Hardware:</strong> Each strap comes equipped with heavy-duty buckles and the necessary mounting hardware for a secure, long-lasting fit.</li> <li><strong>Professional Grade:</strong> Constructed from resilient materials designed to endure the high-stress environment of professional drywall and construction work.</li> <li><strong>All-Inclusive Kit:</strong> Comes with two of each strap type (leg, arch, and toe) along with the required screws and washers for a complete overhaul.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | SKU | SURSS1011B |<br /> | Compatibility | S2, S2X Stilts |<br /> | Color | Black |<br /> | Included Components | 2x Leg Band Straps (HS164S-B), 2x Arch Straps (HS107W-B), 2x Toe Straps (HS108W-B) |<br /> | Hardware Included | Yes (Screws and Washers) |</p>","S2/S2X Stilts Strap Kit, Black (Pair). Includes: (2) Leg Band Straps w/ Buckle (HS164S-B), (2) Arch Straps w/ Buckle, Screws and Washers (HS107W-B), (2) Toe Straps w/ Buckle, Screws and Washers...",,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss1011b.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,"drywall stilts, SurPro",1456,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS1003,,SurPro Super Grip Floor Plate Kit,simple,"<h2>Elevate Your Stability and Safety</h2> <p>Experience uncompromising traction and confidence while working at height with the SurPro Super Grip Floor Plate Kit. Engineered for professionals who demand reliability, these replacement floor plates feature advanced high-friction soles designed to minimize slippage on a variety of job site surfaces. Whether you are navigating smooth concrete or finished flooring, this kit ensures your stilts maintain a secure, stable foundation throughout your workday.</p> <h2>Precision Engineering for Seamless Integration</h2> <p>Designed with the end-user in mind, this kit provides a perfect fit for both single-sided and double-sided SurPro stilt models. The robust construction ensures long-lasting durability, standing up to the rigorous demands of daily construction, drywall, and painting tasks. By replacing worn-out plates with this high-performance kit, you restore the original factory-grade grip and balance of your equipment, keeping you productive and secure.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Enhanced Traction:</strong> Specialized Super Grip soles provide superior surface contact to prevent accidental slips.</li> <li><strong>Universal Compatibility:</strong> Fully compatible with SurPro S1 and S2 stilt series, including both single and double-sided configurations.</li> <li><strong>Professional Durability:</strong> Built to withstand heavy-duty use in demanding industrial and residential environments.</li> <li><strong>Easy Installation:</strong> Designed for quick, hassle-free replacement to minimize downtime on the job.</li> <li><strong>Complete Set:</strong> Includes a pair of floor plates, ensuring both stilts are upgraded simultaneously for balanced performance.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | Product Name | Super Grip Floor Plate Kit |<br /> | SKU | SURSS1003 |<br /> | Compatibility | SurPro S1 &amp; S2 (Single &amp; Double Sided) |<br /> | Quantity | 1 Pair |<br /> | Material | High-Friction Composite/Metal |</p>","Floor Plate Kit w/ Super Grip Soles (Pair). Fits Single Sided Stilts and Double Sided Stilts, models S1 & S2.",,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss1003.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,SurPro,1457,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS1008,,SurPro Wing Bolt Kit,simple,"<h2>Secure Your Stability with SurPro Precision</h2> <p>Maintain the structural integrity of your drywall stilts with the SurPro Wing Bolt Kit. Engineered to provide a rock-solid connection, these replacement bolts are designed to prevent the common issue of loosening during high-intensity work. By utilizing specialized stop and spring washers, this kit ensures a firm, reliable grip that protects your equipment's main body from unnecessary wear and tear.</p> <h2>Engineered for Reliability</h2> <p>As the pioneers of the signature Double Wing Bolt System, SurPro understands that stability is the foundation of professional performance. These high-grade replacement bolts are built to withstand the rigors of daily job site use, ensuring your stilts remain locked in position for maximum safety and confidence while working at height.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Integrated Washer System:</strong> Each bolt features a specialized stop/spring washer combination to prevent loosening and protect the stilt frame.</li> <li><strong>Genuine SurPro Quality:</strong> Designed specifically for compatibility with SurPro stilt models to ensure a perfect fit.</li> <li><strong>Enhanced Durability:</strong> Constructed to resist vibration and mechanical stress, keeping your equipment secure throughout the workday.</li> <li><strong>Versatile Compatibility:</strong> Suitable for various SurPro stilt sizes, allowing for a quick and easy maintenance refresh.</li> <li><strong>Complete Kit:</strong> Includes 4 wing bolts and 4 matching washers per pack to get your equipment back in service immediately.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | SKU | SURSS1008 |<br /> | Kit Contents | 4 Wing Bolts, 4 Washers |<br /> | Compatibility | SurPro Stilt Systems |<br /> | Washer Type | Stop/Spring Washer Combo |</p>",Not all Wing Bolts used on stilts are created equal.,,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss1008.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,SurPro,1458,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
SurPro,SURSS1005FB,,SurPro Wraparound Leg Band Kit w/ Black Strap,simple,"<h2>Elevate Your Stability and Performance</h2> <p>Experience superior support and reliability with the SurPro Wraparound Leg Band Kit. Engineered for professionals who demand precision and durability on the job, this comprehensive set provides everything necessary to secure your stilts with confidence. By utilizing high-grade components, this kit ensures a snug, ergonomic fit that minimizes fatigue and maximizes control during extended periods of use.</p> <h2>Professional-Grade Construction</h2> <p>This kit is designed to withstand the rigors of daily construction and drywall work. Each component is selected for its structural integrity, ensuring that your equipment remains stable and responsive. The included black straps offer a sleek, professional aesthetic while providing the tension required for a secure, non-slip experience. Whether you are performing routine maintenance or upgrading your current setup, this hardware package delivers the consistency and peace of mind required for high-stakes projects.</p> <h2>Key Features</h2> <ul> <li><strong>Complete Integration:</strong> Includes a full set of wraparound bands, heavy-duty straps, and all necessary mounting hardware for a seamless installation.</li> <li><strong>Enhanced Ergonomics:</strong> Designed to distribute pressure evenly, reducing discomfort during long shifts.</li> <li><strong>Durable Hardware:</strong> The included bolt kit features corrosion-resistant fasteners, washers, and nuts to ensure a long-lasting, secure connection.</li> <li><strong>Universal Compatibility:</strong> Engineered specifically for SurPro systems to guarantee a perfect fit and optimal performance.</li> <li><strong>Professional Aesthetic:</strong> Features sleek black straps that maintain a clean, professional look on the job site.</li> </ul> <h2>Technical Specifications</h2> <p>| Specification | Detail |<br /> | :--- | :--- |<br /> | Brand | SurPro |<br /> | SKU | SURSS1005FB |<br /> | Included Bands | 2 x Wraparound Leg Bands (HS101W-F) |<br /> | Included Straps | 2 x Black Leg Band Straps (HS104S-B) |<br /> | Included Hardware | 4 x Bolts, 8 x Washers, 4 x Nuts (SS134) |<br /> | Quantity | 1 Pair |</p>","Wraparound Leg Band Kit (Pair). Includes: (2) Wraparound Leg Bands (HS101W-F), (2) Black Leg Band Straps (HS104S-B), Leg Band Bolt Kit - (4) Bolts, (8) Washers and (4) Nuts (SS134).",,,https://drywalltoolbox.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SurPro/Products/surss1005fb.webp,Stilts & Accessories > SurPro > Stilt Accessories,SurPro,1459,1,0,visible,,,taxable,,1,,,0,0,,,,,1,,,,,,,,,,,Brand,SurPro,1,1
